description: Jinnouchi Wabisuke is a handsome and sardonic 41-year-old computer expert and the "first love" of Natsuki. He is the illegitimate son of Natsuki`s grandfather but was adopted by Sakae, whom Wabisuke cares for deeply. He is the designer of the hacking virus troubling the Oz World.
name: Jinnouchi Wabisuke
